questions.quote: Honey, we were at this beautiful place, and I-I-I just put our names down for fun! I mean, what's the harm in that?
You just did it again. Chandler, your feelings for Chandler are certainly gone!
Hey, I went by the photo shop, take a look, here is a mockup of our card. What do you think?
Pheebs, Monica tripped me, I don't think I can ever run again, ever!
Well, any how, some how I got pregnant, and, and I was scared. I was stupid and sellfish, and I was 18 years old. I mean, you remember what it's like to be eighteen years old?
That's a good thing actually, because ah, he used to have me rehearse with him.
Ross! I think she is trying to make something happen with you to get back at me!
I've actually ruined this haven't I? It's time for the good ice cream now, right?
Yeah, it's like someone literally wrote down my worst nightmare and then charged me $32 to see it!
